{"tid":2069000,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試呢個   吸引蚊的聲頻","createTime":"2020-06-18T05:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T05:46:03.000Z","uid":223067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1880100744c09c8959ec9cef6d2db30f2667b79b","tid":2069000,"uid":223067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HrND868sBZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHrND868sBZQ&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=ed180d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HrND868sBZQ</a><br />\n<br />\n岩岩捉左隻蚊試，好似好少會去有聲個邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oAGtgbh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoAGtgbh.jpg&h=a74cb502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但捉之前我放條聲帶 之後就有隻蚊黎吸血係撥極都唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後捉左之後發現有6～8個位已經被針左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知係純粹餓定真係關條聲帶事<br />\n<br />\n之後再冇蚊黎，唔知係咪冇哂定點樣<br />\n有冇人試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}